title: My first alphabet
creator_credit: Debney Park Secondary College, Gene Geoffrey, Colin Read and Jenny Cocks
brief_description: A colourful and engaging animated alphabet with an Oz flavour to it suitable for young children between the ages 3 to 6. The claymation characters were created and designed by all the students from Year 8/9 Art and Design, Debney Park Secondary College.
